		Standalone Setup (Single machine):
										1. Download selenium-server-4.43.0.jar and place it somewhere. open cmd run this command ==> java -jar selenium-server-4.43.0.jar standalone
										2. Run below command cmd to start Selenium Grid ==>> java -jar selenium-server-4.43.0.jar standalone  
										3. URL to see sessions: http://localhost:4444
		Hub & Node Setup (Multiple machines):
										1. Download selenium-server-4.15.0.jar and place it somewhere in both (hub & node) the machines.
										2. Run below command to make machine as hub
										java -jar selenium-server-4.15.0.jar hub
										3. Run below command to make machine as node ===>> java -jar selenium-server-4.43.0.jar node -- hub http://<hub-ip>:4444
										4. URL to see sessions: http://localhost:4444/
										
